    "description": {
      "value": "<section class=\"secret\">\n<p><strong>After 1 minute</strong>, the diseased creature's skin becomes translucent and slimy, the creature can't regain hit points unless it is underwater, and the disease can be removed only by heal or another disease-curing spell of 6th level or higher. When the creature is <strong>outside a body of water</strong>, it takes&nbsp;<strong>6 (1d12) acid&nbsp;damage every 10 minutes</strong> unless moisture is applied to the skin before 10 minutes have passed.</p>\n</section>\n<p>You feel a surging pain rushing through your body!</p>",
